name: Genesis
description:
Before everything, the very first creation of the almighty God is something really beatifull, shining, a pure light. Really pure from God itself. And far away later, it will be the GENESIS of the universe and all things.

fyi : Every religions mentions this but most of them do not know the essential of it. They called it with various name. Muslims called it "Nur Muhammad", Christians called it "Holy Spirit", Hindus called it "Atman", Buddhis called it "Bodhi Citta" and so on.
